"msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b13ce7b4a37a2f39d5d80e7ad2ba1347bba21d49","tid":509924,"uid":74981,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻男人扮女人，鐵證如山，本癲狗發現左之後，知道原來自己係同緊一個變態人妖溝通，已懊悔不已，所以決定拆穿佢既罪行，免得各位受騙:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻曾經被一向撐開佢既契仔鄭俊弘 (宜家改左名叫鄭欣宜)同其他會員篤爆佢係肥佬扮女人:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s10.postimg.org/eq8erqgi1/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-54-22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs10.postimg.org%2Feq8erqgi1%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-54-22.png&h=99e1c7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/mhshwom03/Screenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fmhshwom03%2FScreenshot_2017-06-11-09-42-18.png&h=2dcd081b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">繼續去死撐啦，同快D用假膠黎掩飾啦傻鳩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aada88bc556798f3f70cf0644da00372ea940e0e","tid":509924,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"2條垃圾係度嘈<img src=\"/as